{"tid":1604713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日我己經決定奮身作戰","createTime":"2019-09-30T05:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T07:22:41.000Z","uid":143023,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7f12066b23821f8ac8531e52e27707d3634b8f8e","tid":1604713,"uid":143023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:07:21.000Z","msg":"我己經當聽日係 運動成敗嘅關鍵<br />\n我會奮不顧身 做到自己能力最大嘅野<br />\n我熱愛香港 熱愛生命 前途生命 我絕不會輕易放入<br />\n但 唯獨香港 我土身土長嘅地方 我唔會放棄 願意揭盡所能 保護佢<br />\n<br />\n同時 小弟希望各位 後排 幫手保充魔力<br />\n火魔力 水魔力 呢啲不在話下<br />\n我要大家唔係十幾隻畜生沖出黎就退<br />\n試下面對佢地<br />\n人多好辦事<br />\n<br />\n求下大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b31dd88b2de57f5333758d473a8873f47f922f","tid":1604713,"uid":220695,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:11:24.000Z","msg":"留返條命 煲底見<br />\n唔準出事"},{"pid":"891c962636f291c4b59c24b0c6e561753d1cc594","tid":1604713,"uid":172500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f242b1c8ff1ca82f066723bb6566c69d0ac17a30","tid":1604713,"uid":323520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:15:38.000Z","msg":"一個都不能少<br />\n我地唔係求死，係求生"},{"pid":"8d4297e65b040b098ab8ac10081f40e92f667e9f","tid":1604713,"uid":203332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:15:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33f55deb3a066557567a0713833c055df0e9db47","tid":1604713,"uid":224869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:18:23.000Z","msg":"徵哨<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/pigeonpatrol\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fpigeonpatrol&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1UUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=0524ef99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/pigeonpatrol</a>"},{"pid":"c668ead74f9cbb88ff04a3a044b346bfed9823bc","tid":1604713,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:35:06.000Z","msg":"no one left behind<br />\n一定要留住條命"},{"pid":"4a524c3d12b2aa10dc67a5b09c54a5ae7d38e3a6","tid":1604713,"uid":220066,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:36:56.000Z","msg":"經過咗三個月既香城足球隊我地都唔係大勝而回<br />\n反而敵方不斷改變踢波策略，導致手足輸左200比0。<br />\n所以我有以下嘅提議，唔知道可唔可行<br />\n歡迎所有參與玩香城足球隊朋友齊齊討論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陣營上有些少改變<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔知道有無效，大家一齊討論，為香城足球隊爭光，其他足球隊都支持緊大家</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">驅逐共黨，還我香港</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"937c444b23a323376c3f2dafaa6f7a87f75adfe8","tid":1604713,"uid":120658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:38:07.000Z","msg":"聽日會係重要既一役，但不是最後一戰<br />\n<br />\n手足，記住不被捕阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d839cf465103a7143f906580525efe8d3b51217a","tid":1604713,"uid":143023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:20:57.000Z","msg":"真係希望大家 講得出做得到<br />\n多謝大家鼓勵<br />\n真係真係要大家嘅support 不論 心理 物資 魔力上<br />\n見畜生試出說唔洗退 打狗！！！"},{"pid":"eae334ebadda202be87c347e45f28ea779fdbc98","tid":1604713,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:22:41.000Z","msg":"和理非都一人一個空啤酒樽係手，班狗一定唔敢衝，是但幾個真係魔法師都夠嚇"}]}